Covert Skins.name: AWP | Containment Breach
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to depict mutated rats trying to escape a radioactive, neon green forest.
Covert Skins.lore: Who knows what radioactive diseases they carry…

Covert Skins.name: MAC-10 | Stalker
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a neon blue cat and yellow and black stripes.

Classified Skins.name: Tec-9 | Decimator
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with totally radical blue and pink highlights.

Classified Skins.name: SSG 08 | Bloodshot
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a monstrosity comprised of green tentacles, teeth, and one eyeball.
Classified Skins.lore: All the better to see you with

Classified Skins.name: SG 553 | Colony IV
Classified Skins.desc: A skeletal red ant has been hand painted above gas masks and an orange-yellow current.
Classified Skins.lore: Become a part of their world

Restricted Skins.name: AK-47 | Rat Rod
Restricted Skins.desc: Recovered from a wasteland junkyard, its original blue topcoat has been painted over, etched into, and weathered away.

Restricted Skins.name: PP-Bizon | Embargo
Restricted Skins.desc: Pieced together from found items, it has a teal base and various 1950's Havana advertisements.

Restricted Skins.name: P2000 | Obsidian
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to look like it was submerged in lava and is solidifying into obsidian as it cools.
Restricted Skins.lore: Giving the term "glass cannon" a whole new meaning

Restricted Skins.name: AUG | Arctic Wolf
Restricted Skins.desc: A custom paint job has been applied which resembles the white coat of an arctic wolf.

Restricted Skins.name: MP7 | Neon Ply
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been laminated and filled with every neon color imaginable.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MP5-SD | Acid Wash
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Prior to assembly its metallic blue topcoat was exposed to acid. It has been finished with brass hardware.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Black and blue and brass all over

Mil-Spec Skins.name: R8 Revolver | Memento
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: The luxury of its ivory grip pairs well with the intricate metalwork on the frame, barrel, and cylinder.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: SCAR-20 | Torn
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been spray-painted with a randomized stripe pattern.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Nova | Plume
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Custom painted brown feathers overlay a wooden receiver and stock.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Dual Berettas | Balance
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A red rose has been painted on either grip over a black base and silver filigree.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: M249 | Warbird
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Originally blue with a yellow heat shield, age and use have taken their toll on its appearance.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: This old bird deserves a rest

Mil-Spec Skins.name: G3SG1 | Black Sand
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a tan and black military camo pattern.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: The Coalition Taskforce was winning, so Mikah turned to a more... aggressive approach
